The error _ValueError: Cannot feed value of shape (100, 2048) for Tensor 'pool_3/reshape:0
', which has shape '(1, 2048)' still occurs for the current build #202 (08.06.2017 02:25:00) (tensorflow 1.2.0 rc1) on Windows 7.

Edit: For the flower image data from the official tutorial as well as for normalized custom images (same size, same color depth).
